text: The Basque Wikipedia (Euskarazko Wikipedia or Euskal Wikipedia in Basque) is the Basque-language edition of Wikipedia. This edition was started in December 2001. It is the 34th largest edition.Wikimedia list of Wikipedias and their statistics.. Retrieved 25 October 2015. As of July 2013, it has over 152,000 articles.List of Wikipedias on Meta-Wiki. ==References== ==Other websites== *Basque Wikipedia main page Category:Wikipedias Category:Websites established in 2001 Wikipedia
